# Per-PR entries now land as unique files under docs/changelog.d/ (assembled into
# docs/CHANGELOG.md at release time), so concurrent PRs no longer collide here. This
# union driver is kept only as a fallback for the rare *direct* edit of this file — a
# cut-release squash — and note it helps local merges only: GitHub's mergeability check
# and merge button ignore .gitattributes merge drivers. See docs/changelog.d/README.md.
docs/CHANGELOG.md merge=union

